    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a practical choice for anyone needing a reliable daily driver. The exterior exhibits clear signs of its age, including several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading in the paint on the hood. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear with a few small stains, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs consistently, though it may require some minor maintenance in the near future to address typical wear-and-tear items. It is a solid, honest vehicle that is ready for the road.",
