      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and remains a reliable choice for daily transportation. The engine starts consistently and the car is currently in running order, though it shows clear signs of its age and would benefit from a comprehensive tune-up and some routine maintenance to ensure long-term dependability. You can expect some cosmetic wear on both the interior and exterior, as well as minor mechanical quirks typical of a car with this history. It is a solid, functional vehicle for someone looking for a budget-friendly option that is ready to drive today.",
      "price": 19500.0,
